OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference at
OL,7,FSealands Farm in Bridgend, the Cabinet
OL,8,FSecretary thanked farmers for their
OL,9,F"candour", saying that the change of
OL,10,Ftimings was part of his "commitment to
OL,11,Fmeaningful engagement with the farming
OL,12,Fsector."
OL,14,FHe said: "Since the first day of
OL,15,Ftaking up this role I have been out
OL,16,Fand about meeting and listening to our
OL,17,Ffarmers, hearing their views and
OL,18,Ftaking on board what they have to say.
