OL,7,Fengagement with the farming sector,
OL,8,FPlaid Cymru colleagues under the
OL,9,FCooperation Agreement and other
OL,10,Fstakeholders on the changes needed
OL,11,Fwill necessitate a change in the
OL,12,Fimplementation timetable.
OL,14,F"We have always said the Scheme would
OL,15,Fnot be introduced until it is ready
OL,16,Fand I stand by that."
