OL,6,FHe then confirmed that the Basic
OL,7,FPayment Scheme would continue to be
OL,8,Favailable in 2025, with the proposed
OL,9,FSFS (Sustainable Farming Scheme)
OL,10,Ftransition period starting from 2026,
OL,11,Fwith an announcement to follow on the
OL,12,FBPS ceiling.
OL,14,FExisting rural investment schemes,
OL,15,Fsuch as the small grants schemes, will
OL,16,Fcontinue to support infrastructure
OL,17,Fchanges, say the Welsh government.
