OL,6,FThe government also claimed they will
OL,7,Falso work on a new landscape scale
OL,8,Fscheme which will build on the
OL,9,Fexperience of previous collaboration
OL,10,Fschemes.
OL,12,FThis new timeframe will give the
OL,13,Fopportunity to work through a number
OL,14,Fof important aspects.
OL,16,FBack in February, thousands of farmers
OL,17,Fdescended on the to protest against
OL,18,Fthe controversial proposals, which see
OL,19,Ffarmers having to meet strict
OL,20,Fenvironmental targets in return for
OL,21,Fgovernment funding.
