OL,3,CControversial farming scheme delayed
OL,4,Cby a year say Welsh Government
OL,6,F"The farmers I speak to have major
OL,7,Fconcerns about tree planting, common
OL,8,Fland, tenant farmers, and we need to
OL,9,Fhave more detail from the cabinet
OL,10,Fsecretary over amendments he is going
OL,11,Fto make to the scheme to make sure we
OL,12,Fhave something that works for our
OL,13,Ffarmers, and not against them, and
OL,14,Fsafeguards the future of the industry."
OL,16,FPlaid Cymru said it welcomed the
OL,17,F"pragmatic and sensible approach" of
OL,18,Fthe new Cabinet Secretary for Rural
OL,19,FAffairs.
