OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's Rural Affairs
OL,7,Fspokesperson Llyr Gruffydd MS, said:
OL,9,F"We've always said that the one-size-
OL,10,Ffits-all figure of 10% tree cover will
OL,11,Fnot work for many farm types and farm
OL,12,Flocations.
OL,14,F"There is now a recognition that this
OL,15,Fneeds flexibility and that other ways
OL,16,Fof capturing carbon must be considered.
