OL,6,FI urge the Government to ensure that
OL,7,Fthe Roundtable which will consider
OL,8,Falternative approaches includes those
OL,9,Fwith farming experience. They are the
OL,10,Fones who know best what will work on
OL,11,Fthe ground."
OL,13,FA spokesperson from WWF Cymru called
OL,14,Fthe development "disappointing."
OL,16,F"It's deeply worrying. The nature and
OL,17,Fclimate emergencies aren't going to
OL,18,Flet up", said Policy and Advocacy
OL,19,FManager Alexander Phillips.
