OL,4,Cby a year say Welsh Government
OL,6,F"We already know that extreme weather
OL,7,Fevents linked to climate change are
OL,8,Fcosting Welsh farmers tens of millions
OL,9,Fof pounds a year, and one of the
OL,10,Fprimary aims of this scheme was to
OL,11,Fhelp farmers combat climate change and
OL,12,Fmitigate its impacts.
OL,14,F"So the delay in this scheme will
OL,15,Flengthen action and damage
OL,16,Fopportunities to get towards our
OL,17,Fnational targets such as net zero."
OL,19,FMore to follow...
